        {
            "heading": "Aim",
            "content":[
                {
                    "type":"paragraph",
                    "text":"To reveal unconscious gender biases through a profession-gender matching exercise."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Learning Outcomes",
            "content":[
                {
                    "type":"bullet",
                    "text":"To engage participants in a matching exercise that challenges gender stereotypes."
                },
                {
                    "type":"bullet",
                    "text":"To start a discussion on the idea of women being employed in non-traditional professions."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Materials Required",
            "content":[
                {
                    "type":"paragraph",
                    "text":"Printed copy of the profession-gender matching exercise table for each participant."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Sequence",
            "content":[
                {
                    "type":"bold",
                    "text":"Step 1: "
                },
                {
                    "type":"paragraph",
                    "text":"Distribute the profession-gender matching exercise table to each participant."
                },
                {
                    "type":"bold",
                    "text":"Step 2: "
                },
                {
                    "type":"paragraph",
                    "text":"Instruct the participants to tick the box consisting of the gender they believe would be most suited for each profession."
                },
                {
                    "type":"bold",
                    "text":"Step 3: "
                },
                {
                    "type":"paragraph",
                    "text":"Initiate a discussion about the choices made and the assumptions behind them."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Evaluation",
            "content":[
                {
                    "type":"paragraph",
                    "text":"Assess the depth of the discussion and the perceptions shared about gender roles and stereotypes."
                },
